    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You may use an action and spend </span><strong>@LOSS[5 mp]</strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\"> to perform an Opposed </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>INS + WLP</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Check against a creature that can hear and understand you — describe your accusations! If you succeed, the target loses </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>SL × 10</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Mind Points and suffers </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>@EFFECT[dazed] </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">or</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong> @EFFECT[shaken] </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">(your choice).</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You gain a bonus equal to </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>SL</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">to your </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>INS + WLP</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Checks for this Skill.</span> </p><hr /><p>Skill Level <strong>1</strong> - Target loses <strong>@LOSS[10 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>2</strong> - Target loses <strong>@LOSS[20 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>3</strong> - Target loses <strong>@LOSS[30 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>4</strong> - Target loses <strong>@LOSS[40 mp]</strong></p>",
